Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 那邊真的很熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實很吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是里見或尾崎帶進來的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好奇那個莉芳特意邀請來的重要客人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.22,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.22,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:43.62,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:43.62,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:48.09,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:48.09,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:54.40,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:54.40,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹著乾燥的風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:01:00.87,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:01:00.87,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真偽 銘刻於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:04.28,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:04.28,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈願待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:06.85,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:06.85,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愛過 恨過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:10.35,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:10.35,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲傷最後化作溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:15.32,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:15.32,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入無盡黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:20.09,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:20.09,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍會尋覓明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:24.40,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:24.40,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃燒的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.40,0:01:29.47,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.40,0:01:29.47,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之緣 最終轉化成奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:31.67,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:31.67,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:34.14,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:34.14,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:37.88,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:37.88,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撥開黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:41.71,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:41.71,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追尋你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:43.98,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:43.98,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:47.62,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:47.62,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總有一天 命運將會轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:52.29,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:52.29,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要讓眼淚白流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:56.93,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:56.93,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交織騷動的盡頭
